There was a shootout
in the Langa Township.

812
01:21:37,229 --> 01:21:40,266
Two crime scenes. One at the
residence of Carlos Villar.

813
01:21:40,332 --> 01:21:41,867
He's a document forger.

814
01:21:41,934 --> 01:21:43,571
The other in
a nearby tenement.

815
01:21:43,636 --> 01:21:44,773
And where was
Frost last seen?

816
01:21:44,837 --> 01:21:45,940
Tenement.

817
01:21:46,838 --> 01:21:47,975
Have fun at Villar's.

818
01:21:48,039 --> 01:21:49,642
We'll meet up later.

819
01:22:09,858 --> 01:22:11,859
You were right
about Ana.

820
01:22:13,962 --> 01:22:15,565
That's her name.

821
01:22:18,132 --> 01:22:19,542
Sorry to hear that.

822
01:22:21,869 --> 01:22:26,544
Most case officers get
married three, four times.

823
01:22:28,675 --> 01:22:30,347
You?

824
01:22:33,046 --> 01:22:34,649
Once.

825
