837
01:23:45,576 --> 01:23:48,954
The husband,
he was a whistleblower.

838
01:23:50,113 --> 01:23:52,820
The whole thing was about

839
01:23:52,882 --> 01:23:56,454
stopping him from
testifying about wet works

