848
01:24:30,815 --> 01:24:33,590
Yeah, I used to be
innocent like you.

849
01:24:33,651 --> 01:24:36,426
Wrap myself up
in the flag...

850
01:24:43,826 --> 01:24:45,805
I'm going to take you in.

851
01:24:54,402 --> 01:24:55,971
Good for you.

852
01:25:50,184 --> 01:25:51,287
Barlow.

853
01:25:51,352 --> 01:25:53,228
LINKLATER ON PHONE Witnesses
identified a pair of men

854
01:25:53,288 --> 01:25:55,130
fitting Weston and
Frost's description

855
01:25:55,189 --> 01:25:57,225
leaving this
location together.

856
01:25:57,391 --> 01:25:58,630
So, he pulled it off.

857
01:25:58,692 --> 01:26:01,570
Weston is aiding and
abetting a fugitive.

858
01:26:01,895 --> 01:26:03,066
You're wrong.

859
01:26:03,130 --> 01:26:05,735
If he's with Frost, he's
taking him to the safe house.

860
01:26:05,798 --> 01:26:07,606
That's where we got to be.

861
01:26:08,067 --> 01:26:09,636
Fine. Fine.

862
01:26:09,802 --> 01:26:12,543
Meet me at the crossroads
at Old Malmesbury Road.

863
01:26:39,594 --> 01:26:40,970
Who are you?

864
01:26:41,830 --> 01:26:43,103
You Weston?

865
01:26:44,766 --> 01:26:46,369
Give me the shotgun.

866
01:26:46,434 --> 01:26:48,037
