he killed Keller.

945
01:36:56,468 --> 01:36:57,605
No.

946
01:36:59,771 --> 01:37:01,374
I killed Keller.

947
01:37:09,847 --> 01:37:12,122
Frost killed Keller.

948
01:37:14,150 --> 01:37:16,493
