watching your every move?

959
01:38:04,695 --> 01:38:07,470
Some maybe
you're not proud of.

960
01:38:07,531 --> 01:38:11,000
And you will have some you're
not proud of, believe me.

961
01:38:11,067 --> 01:38:13,603
And then tries to
use it against you?

962
01:38:16,204 --> 01:38:18,376
You would do
what you have to do.

963
01:38:19,241 --> 01:38:21,652
You would do
what you have to do.

964
01:38:28,582 --> 01:38:30,254
Where's the file?

965
