969
01:40:52,175 --> 01:40:53,517
Let's go.

970
01:41:16,429 --> 01:41:18,032
We got him.

971
01:41:20,300 --> 01:41:21,471
A hell of a job.

972
01:41:56,965 --> 01:41:58,375
You smell that?

973
