Local grape.
Pinotage is great...

975
01:42:13,412 --> 01:42:15,823
I don't want you
losing this one.

976
01:42:16,382 --> 01:42:19,294
It's worth a lot
of money.

977
01:42:22,587 --> 01:42:25,066
You're a good boy,
Matty.

978
01:42:27,425 --> 01:42:29,097
You know what you are.

979
01:42:32,463 --> 01:42:33,805
Hey.

980
01:42:34,798 --> 01:42:36,708
I know what you're not.

981
01:42:40,904 --> 01:42:43,076
You're better than me.

982
01:42:46,875 --> 01:42:51,619
No, it's okay,
just be better than me.

983
01:42:56,317 --> 01:42:58,057
You promise me.

984
01:42:59,487 --> 01:43:00,760
Yeah.

985
01:43:06,359 --> 01:43:08,668
Well, let's...

986
01:43:10,996 --> 01:43:12,702
Let's go.

987
01:43:14,099 --> 01:43:17,602
I just got to get up.
I need to get up.

988
01:43:19,837 --> 01:43:20,906
Stay.

989
01:43:23,675 --> 01:43:24,846
Stay.

990
01:43:27,945 --> 01:43:29,184
Hey...

991
01:44:45,580 --> 01:44:49,083
That's exactly
as it happened.

992
01:44:53,754 --> 01:44:55,494
Obviously,
this situation needs

993
01:44:55,554 --> 01:44:57,794
to be handled with a
certain amount of finesse.

994
01:44:58,291 --> 01:44:59,963
Has anybody else
seen this report?

995
01:45:00,026 --> 01:45:01,936
No, sir. Not yet.

996
01:45:03,261 --> 01:45:04,898
Matt, I'm sure this
comes as no surprise,

997
01:45:04,963 --> 01:45:09,638
but parts of this report are going to
have to be altered for national security.

998
01:45:10,968 --> 01:45:12,412
Which parts, sir?

999
01:45:12,469 --> 01:45:13,879
Well...

1000
01:45:14,471 --> 01:45:16,541
David Barlow can't
be held responsible

1001
01:45:16,607 --> 01:45:18,483
for what happened
to the safe house.

1002
01:45:19,309 --> 01:45:21,914
We just don't
need the scandal.

1003
01:45:21,978 --> 01:45:24,480
But, sir, you and I both know
that, that is just not the truth.

1004
01:45:24,547 --> 01:45:27,152
People don't want
the truth anymore, Matt.

1005
01:45:27,215 --> 01:45:30,127
It's too messy.
Keeps them up nights.

1006
01:45:34,356 --> 01:45:36,665
I'll tell you what I am
willing to do, though.

1007
01:45:37,491 --> 01:45:40,596
I think the Agency has
grossly underestimated you,

1008
01:45:40,661 --> 01:45:44,802
and I'm recommending you for a
senior case officer position.

1009
01:45:44,864 --> 01:45:46,365
Provided you still want it.

1010
01:45:47,300 --> 01:45:49,939
That's a generous
offer, sir.

1011
01:45:51,036 --> 01:45:54,778
There's just one thing you
need to clarify for me.

1012
01:45:54,840 --> 01:45:56,147
Of course.

1013
01:45:57,209 --> 01:46:00,246
Frost may have been
carrying some vital intel.

1014
01:46:00,311 --> 01:46:01,653
A file.

1015
01:46:02,213 --> 01:46:05,091
I'm not seeing that
anywhere in this report.

1016
01:46:12,522 --> 01:46:14,330
What was
on the file, sir?

1017
01:46:14,391 --> 01:46:17,132
Something that, quite frankly,
could be very damaging

1018
01:46:17,193 --> 01:46:19,536
to the Agency
and to our allies.

1019
01:46:22,698 --> 01:46:26,839
I don't see why Frost would even
mention something like that to me.

1020
01:46:32,072 --> 01:46:34,517
No, I suppose he wouldn't,
would he?

1021
01:46:38,879 --> 01:46:42,155
You realize, though,
that if that file did leak,

1022
01:46:43,683 --> 01:46:45,821
what would happen
to the person responsible?

1023
01:46:45,885 --> 01:46:47,886
That person would
be arrested, sir.

1024
01:46:47,953 --> 01:46:49,795
He'd be risking
everything.

1025
01:46:50,822 --> 01:46:54,633
He'd have enemies in every
intelligence agency in the world.

1026
01:46:56,260 --> 01:46:59,832
In the eyes of the CIA he'd
be just like Tobin Frost.

1027
01:47:03,634 --> 01:47:06,580
Frost didn't say anything
about a file, sir.

1028
01:47:11,808 --> 01:47:13,150
All right, son.

1029
01:47:14,276 --> 01:47:15,879
Take a few days off.

1030
01:47:15,944 --> 01:47:17,923
We'll get you
started next week.

1031
01:47:19,748 --> 01:47:21,090
Thank you.

1032
01:47:23,284 --> 01:47:26,264
And think about our
conversation, would you?

1033
01:47:26,521 --> 01:47:28,022
Will do.

1034
01:47:28,089 --> 01:47:30,066
I'll take it
from here, sir.

